::Annihilator/Killer/Zeus::

Annihilator fires yet more shots at Snow Tech, a missile from his missile 
launcher and many shots from his gun.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killer jumps at Shadow Cat, firing a rocket at her from his missile launcher.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Seeing that all his brothers have returned to the battlefield, Zeus lands, 
prepairing to combine with them to form Divine Presence (I forgot what we 
decided to call it, guys).

"Quickly, brother," he says over his comm-link to Ares, Anubis, Ra, and 
Hades, "Let us combine and crush these pathetic fools!"
